{"lemma":"حُمَةٌ","slug":"حُمَةٌ","root":"ح.م.#","root_slug":"ح-م-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-م-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9208","n9222"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sting"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħu.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9208","headword_ar":"حُمَةٌ","root":"Hmw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HmY","text_ar":"حمى"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n9222","headword_ar":"حُمَةٌ","root":"HmY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"venom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poison,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Lh, S, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) of a scorpion, (Lth, S,) and of anything that stings or bites: (Lth:) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumawN","text_ar":"حُمَوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumFY","text_ar":"حُمًى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) and IAar mentions"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hum~apN","text_ar":"حُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hm","text_ar":"حم"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sting"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the hornet, (Lth, K,) and of the scorpion, (Lth, IAth,) and the like, (Lth,) and of the serpent; (K;) because the venom comes forth from it: (IAth:) so applied by the vulgar: (Lth:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumaAtN","text_ar":"حُمَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumFY","text_ar":"حُمًى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vehemence"},{"kind":"text","text":"of cold. (K, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","Lh","S","K","IAth"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%A9/","headword_ar":"حمة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_21","lexicon_en":"Muḥammad al-Fattinī, Majmaʿ Biḥār al-Anwār fī Gharāʾib al-Tanzīl wa Laṭāʾif al-Akhbār (d. 1578 CE)","lexicon_ar":"مجمع بحار الأنوار للفَتِّنيّ","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=35317#e556d0","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">[حمة]</span><span> نه فيه: رخص في الرقية من \"الحمة\" وهو بالخفة السم، وقد يشدد ويطلق على إبرة العقرب للمجاورة، لأن السم منها يخرج، واصله حمو أو حمى كصرد والهاء عوض عن لامه المحذوفة. ومنه ح الدجال: وينزع \"حمة\" كل دابة، أي سمها. ك: لا رقية إلا عن عين أو \"حمة\" لا يريد به الحصر وإنما أراد لا أحق بالرقية منهما لشدة الضرر فيهما.</span>"}]}}